videos.description: LeBron James darts a pass quickly down the floor to Montrezl Harrell who goes up to get a quick Lakers bucket before anyone can blink.

videos.description: LeBron James completes a triple-double vs. the Nuggets as he slings a bounce pass to Talen Horton-Tucker from the 3-point line to the baseline for a sweet reverse layup.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (LeBron notches triple-double with sweet pass to THT) 2021/02/04 ESHEET

videos.headline: LeBron notches triple-double with sweet pass to THT

videos.description: Behind LeBron James' triple-double, the Lakers rally from a halftime deficit and roll to a 114-93 win over the Nuggets.
